  <brief_title>Interventional Radiology for the Treatment of Symptomatic Portal Hypertension in Patients With Cavernous Transformation of Portal Vein</brief_title>
  <official_title>Interventional Radiology for the Treatment of Symptomatic Portal Hypertension in Patients With Cavernous Transformation of Portal Vein</official_title>
